				<section id='overview'>
					<hr class='indent' /><h5>Overview</h5>
 
					<p>This is part of currently ongoing research on varying constraints in the design process. Groups presented to narrowed constraints at various stages in the design process yielded varying degress of creative results. Results indicate that those who brainstormed and prototyped before receiving the narrow constraints yielded results that were both more novel and more appropriate than other groups. This research project at the 2013 <a href='http://uist.acm.org'>ACM Symposium on User Interface Software Technology (UIST)</a> in St. Andrews, Scotland. 
					</p>

					<figure>
